<h4>Through the study and practice of shamanic Ritual Arts, individuals learn to live in harmony with nature, Mother Earth and Her children, the animals, plants, minerals and each other.</h4>

[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label="Row"][et_pb_column type="1_2"][et_pb_video admin_label="Video" src="https://youtu.be/Bfoc3jlZHyA"]



[/et_pb_video][et_pb_text admin_label="Text" background_layout="light" text_orientation="left" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]

<h3>ApachetaÂ Ritual</h3>
An apacheta is a sacred stone cairn and acts like an acupuncture needle on Mother Earthâ€™s Energy or nervous system called a Seque System.

Pachakuti Mesa Tradition (PMT) Carriers, Awahoo and Justine, describe how to build a an apacheta in the video below.

[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_2"][et_pb_video admin_label="Video" src="https://youtu.be/-_MUaPlwt_Q"]



[/et_pb_video][et_pb_text admin_label="Text" background_layout="light" text_orientation="left" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid"]

<h3>DespachoÂ Ritual</h3>
A despacho is composed of items called recados, that are infused with prayers, then ceremonially arranged in a beautiful pattern on a large piece of paper. The mandala- like creation is folded into a bundle and ritually offered to the fire or to the earth. <a href="http://heartofthehealer.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/2016-despacho-ritual.pdf">Click here for a PDF</a> document with step by step instructions by Anita Stewart or view the video below created by Awahoo and Justine Ferguson.

[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label="Row" global_module="7835" make_fullwidth="off" use_custom_width="off" width_unit="on" use_custom_gutter="off" custom_padding="|||10px" padding_mobile="off" background_color="#3a69c1" allow_player_pause="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="off" make_equal="off" parallax_1="off" parallax_method_1="off" column_padding_mobile="on" custom_padding_last_edited="on|phone" custom_margin="10px||20px|" custom_margin_last_edited="on|desktop" custom_margin_tablet="||10px|" custom_padding_tablet="5px||0px|5px"][et_pb_column type="4_4"][et_pb_text global_parent="7835" admin_label="Text" background_layout="dark" text_orientation="left" use_border_color="off" border_color="#ffffff" border_style="solid" custom_padding="5px|5px|5px|5px" custom_padding_last_edited="on|tablet" custom_padding_tablet="2px|5px|0px|5px"]

